\c 34
\s Jehovha anobatsira vanotenda kwaari
\d Pisarema raDhavhidhi, panguva yaakazviita benzi pamberi paAbhimereki, akadzingwa naye, akaenda hake.
\p
\v 1 Ndicharumbidza Jehovha nguva dzese; rumbidzo yake ichagara mumuromo mangu.
\v 2 Mweya wangu uchazvirumbidza muna Jehovha; vanyoro vachazvinzwa, vakafara.
\v 3 Kudzai Jehovha pamwe chete neni, ngatikudzise zita rake pamwe chete.
\p
\v 4 Ndakatsvaka Jehovha, akandipindura, akandisunungura pakutya kwangu kwese.
\v 5 Vakatarira kwaari, vakapenyeswa nomufaro; zviso zvavo hazvingatongonyadziswi.
\v 6 Murombo uyu akachema, Jehovha akamunzwa, akamuponesa panjodzi dzake dzese.
\v 7 Mutumwa waJehovha anokomberedza vanomutya, nokuvarwira.
\v 8 Ravirai henyu, muone kuti Jehovha wakanaka; wakakomborerwa munhu anovimba naye.
\v 9 Ityai Jehovha, imwi vatsvene vake; nokuti vanomutya havana chavanoshaiwa.
\v 10 Vana veshumba vanoshaiwa, vanofa nenzara; asi vanotsvaka Jehovha havana chinhu chakanaka chavangashaiwa.
\p
\v 11 Uyai imwi vana, munditeerere; ndichakudzidzisai kutya Jehovha.
\v 12 Ndoupi munhu anoda upenyu, anoda mazuva mazhinji, kuti aone zvakanaka?
\v 13 Dzora rurimi rwako pakutaura zvakaipa, nemiromo yako, urege kutaura zvinonyengera.
\v 14 Ibva pane zvakaipa uite zvakanaka; tsvaka rugare, urutevere.
\v 15 Meso aJehovha anotarira vakarurama, uye nzeve dzake dzinonzwa kuchema kwavo.
\v 16 Chiso chaJehovha chinovenga vanoita zvakaipa, kuti abvise chiyeudziro chavo panyika.
\v 17 Vakarurama vakadana, Jehovha akanzwa, akavarwira panjodzi dzavo dzese.
\v 18 Jehovha ari pedo nevane moyo yakaputsika, anoponesa vane mweya yakapwanyika.
\v 19 Akarurama anamatambudziko mazhinji; asi Jehovha anomurwira abude paari ese.
\v 20 Anochengeta mapfupa ake ese; hakuna nerimwe rawo rinovhuniwa.
\v 21 Zvakaipa zvichauraya akaipa; uye vanovenga vakarurama vachapiwa mhosva.
\v 22 Jehovha anodzikunura mweya yavaranda vake; hapana neumwe kuna vanovimba naye achapiwa mhosva.
